{"title":"新农业税快板  （应征稿之二）","authors":["杨忠铭"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":2,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新农业税快板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（应征稿之二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨忠铭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫老乡，听我言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有件大事谈一谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱区新的农业税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府公布在报端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内容你要不知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我仔细谈一遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地改革大平分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们农民把身翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了土地和农具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就应劳动多生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奖励劳动多生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就得实行新负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民军队大进攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国胜利并不远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决消灭蒋介石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由平等万万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然胜利不很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人自己不会完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命必须打到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得努力支前线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府公布农业税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公私兼顾很周全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证战争的供给，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展农业大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保障劳动的所得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"固定合理的负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁有土地谁纳税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每人除个免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有些土地不纳税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听我把它说一遍："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公路、水渠及河身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民场地和房院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河堤、荒地、林木地、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一般都不出负担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如因偷懒把地荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那可不能在此限。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开垦生荒新修地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免征三年才负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟荒已满六年整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作生荒一样看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年五年的熟荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁再去种也合算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自你再种来开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两年以内不负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山地、新修河滩地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防被水冲难生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有收获那年起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负担免去头三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁和别人轮种地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮到谁种谁负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业税则总方针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奖励劳动多生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业税则很周全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算办法也简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首先定出“标准亩”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照产量来计算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常年产量一市石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就按“标准”一亩算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今后农业的负担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"根据常年产量算；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深耕细作多施肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选用良种多生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管生产怎样多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多收获的不负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管你种甚植物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是种油料或种棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然种这利润大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也按种谷去负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想偷懒不劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁想坐着当懒汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然土地少打粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负担一点不少算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要开渠或凿井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想变旱田为水田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负担三年不增加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍按旱田来计算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修理废渠或废井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恢复原来的水田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二年以内不加税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年开始多负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑园、竹园、果木园、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山货藕池的出产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按着批发平均价，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对半折谷来计算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算办法讲一遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡都要记心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家加油齐努力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发家致富多生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有农业的人员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分老少女和男，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每人除个“标准亩”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免去纳税不负担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着说起来方便，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫做一个免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每人只能除一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里没有空子钻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鳏寡孤独无劳力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军工烈属有困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照顾他们的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才可增加免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣牺牲的烈士、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命军人和职员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要在本人的家中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扣除他的免税点；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果她是女同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经结婚怎么办？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆家娘家谁家扣？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全依本人的自愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有机关的证明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆家扣除免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被人轮流养活的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家扣除免税点？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个不能死规定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮养人们去商谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常年寄居别人家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己另外无财产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家把他来抚养，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家扣除免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里雇的有长工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看在谁家来吃饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分别扣除来计算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如是零碎雇短工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能扣除免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常年在外的人员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活不由家庭管；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本人经营工商业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再扣除免税点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁养牲口为种地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁养幼畜为生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一律给他除消耗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂养牲口有光沾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的消耗怎样扣？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也按“标准亩”计算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛驴扣除四斗整，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骡马扣除谷七斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"负担到底怎样纳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢慢听我谈一谈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全家所有标准亩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扣除消耗免税点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剩下多少标准亩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就按“负担亩”计算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果产量评真实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就能固定派负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算负担的单位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小米为准很方便。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每年一个“负担亩”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十五斤纳负担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有地方的粮款，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县区不能随便＠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每亩至多五市斤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行政公署统一管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全年征收农业税，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏秋两季分别＠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如无夏收的地区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋季一次征收完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便利人民来缴纳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保证供给不困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除缴粮食与花布，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还可缴草和现款，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如遇水、旱、虫、雹灾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缴纳公粮有困难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政府根据实情况，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以缓征或减免。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}